please explain to me how admitting you fucked up and slandered someone is a weakness . where i am from that is a character trait that we associate with strength . anyone can walk away and piss and moan . it takes a man to walk up to someone in front of people that dislike them and admit they fucked up . i may never like that man but you can bet your last dollar i will have respect for him . there is a big difference between backing down from a fight because you are scared to fight and admiting you fucked up . one is cowardice the other is the actions of an honorable person deserving of respect . you have a lot of growing up to do kerra if you truely cant tell the difference . <br>
